      • deposit

        public int deposit​(double amount,
                   boolean isCash)
        Deposit money.
        返回:
        1 if the account has been suspended, 2 if the user successfully deposit with check, and will wait for several minutes before it is issued. 0 if the user successfully deposit with cash, and the money will be directly added to the balance.
